  "summary": "Small, light, fickle lake (avg ~3 kt, gusting ~6, prevailing WSW). The Goldschäkel starts off Immensee at the Chiemen narrows — the tactically complex transition between the two basins. RC sets the marks; the lake long axis (~343°) is the reference course.",
